      "description": "Honest fair-condition car that should make a solid budget daily or project base. It shows normal age and use throughout, with visible cosmetic wear, some imperfections inside and out, and signs that it has been driven rather than pampered. Overall it presents respectably enough for regular use, but buyers should expect an older used vehicle with blemishes, wear items, and the kind of minor needs that often come with a fair-condition car. Good fit for someone who wants something usable and reasonably priced without expecting a showpiece.",
